{"version": 3, "term": {"cols": 132, "rows": 44}, "title": "tael-cli and tael live demo"}
[0.1, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H"]
[1.3, "o", "\r\n  \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557 \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557 \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557\u2588\u2588\u2557\r\n  \u255a\u2550\u2550\u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u255d\u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u2588\u2588\u2557\u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u255d\u2588\u2588\u2551\r\n     \u2588\u2588\u2551   \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2551\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557  \u2588\u2588\u2551\r\n     \u2588\u2588\u2551   \u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u2588\u2588\u2551\u2588\u2588\u2554\u2550\u2550\u255d  \u2588\u2588\u2551\r\n     \u2588\u2588\u2551   \u2588\u2588\u2551  \u2588\u2588\u2551\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2557\r\n     \u255a\u2550\u255d   \u255a\u2550\u255d  \u255a\u2550\u255d\u255a\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u255d\u255a\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u2550\u255d\r\n\r\n  AI-agent-native observability: one tael-cli install, one tael binary\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Install the published package: the crate is tael-cli, the binary is tael.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m cargo binstall tael-cli\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.5, "o", "Resolved package: tael-cli\r\nInstalled binary: tael\r\nRun `tael serve` to start the bundled server.\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# The current CLI exposes server, query, live, eval, and reliability commands.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael --help\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.5, "o", "AI-agent-native observability CLI\r\n\r\nUsage: tael [OPTIONS] <COMMAND>\r\n\r\nCommands:\r\n  serve       Run the tael server: OTLP ingest (gRPC :4317), storage, REST API (:7701)\r\n  query       Query telemetry data\r\n  get         Get a specific resource by ID\r\n  comment     Add or view comments on traces\r\n  services    List known services and their health\r\n  live        Interactive TUI trace feed\r\n  summarize   Aggregated health summary over a time window\r\n  anomalies   Surface services whose error-rate or p95 regressed vs a baseline window\r\n  correlate   Pull spans, logs, and metrics for a trace ID\r\n  watch       Poll the summary endpoint and print deltas between samples\r\n  eval        Collect, score, report, and compare trace-native evals\r\n  issue       Classify production failures into recurring issues\r\n  signal      Define and inspect long-running reliability signals\r\n  experiment  Compare production experiment variants\r\n  diagnose    Record and list untrusted agent self diagnostics\r\n  server      Server management\r\n  skill       Install the tael Claude Code skill\r\n  help        Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)\r\n\r\n...\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Start the embedded tael server: REST API + OTLP ingest + local storage.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael serve\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.6, "o", "tael server starting\r\n  REST API     http://127.0.0.1:7701\r\n  OTLP gRPC    127.0.0.1:4317\r\n  storage      tael-backend\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Health check: commands default to structured JSON for agents.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael server status --format json\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.5, "o", "{\"response\":\"ok\",\"status\":\"healthy\"}\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Seed OpenTelemetry traces from sample services and a gen_ai LLM span.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael-test\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.7, "o", "connecting to tael server at http://127.0.0.1:4317\r\n  sent: healthy API request (3 spans)\r\n  sent: slow database query (2 spans)\r\n  sent: error in payment service (3 spans)\r\n  sent: fan-out to downstream services (4 spans)\r\n  sent: burst of fast requests (10 spans)\r\n  sent: LLM chat request (gen_ai.*) (2 spans)\r\n\r\ndone \u2014 use `tael query traces` or `tael services` to inspect\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Service health is available without opening a dashboard.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael services --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.9, "o", "+----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------+\r\n| Service              | Spans | Traces | Avg Duration (ms) | Error Rate |\r\n+========================================================================+\r\n| api-gateway          | 15    | 15     | 227.3             | 6.67%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| order-service        | 2     | 2      | 450.0             | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| user-service         | 2     | 2      | 42.5              | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| cart-service         | 1     | 1      | 15.0              | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| auth-service         | 1     | 1      | 8.0               | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| notification-service | 1     | 1      | 45.0              | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| llm-proxy            | 1     | 1      | 1790.0            | 0.00%      |\r\n|----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------|\r\n| payment-service      | 1     | 1      | 310.0             | 100.00%    |\r\n+----------------------+-------+--------+-------------------+------------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Query traces, filter by status, attributes, and LLM payload text.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael query traces --status error --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.8, "o", "+---------------+------------------+-----------------+---------------------+---------------+--------+\r\n| Trace ID      | Span ID          | Service         | Operation           | Duration (ms) | Status |\r\n+===================================================================================================+\r\n| 11352dea5f3e\u2026 | f40453715c4508d2 | payment-service | payment.charge      | 310.0         | error  |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-----------------+---------------------+---------------+--------|\r\n| 11352dea5f3e\u2026 | 8abcf7ecfcb48ecd | api-gateway     | HTTP POST /checkout | 340.0         | error  |\r\n+---------------+------------------+-----------------+---------------------+---------------+--------+\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael query traces --attribute http.route=/checkout --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.8, "o", "+---------------+------------------+-------------+---------------------+---------------+--------+\r\n| Trace ID      | Span ID          | Service     | Operation           | Duration (ms) | Status |\r\n+===============================================================================================+\r\n| 11352dea5f3e\u2026 | 8abcf7ecfcb48ecd | api-gateway | HTTP POST /checkout | 340.0         | error  |\r\n+---------------+------------------+-------------+---------------------+---------------+--------+\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael query traces --text \"OTLP\" --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.9, "o", "+---------------+------------------+-------------+----------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------+\r\n| Trace ID      | Span ID          | Service     | Operation      | Duration (ms) | Status | LLM                                  |\r\n+=================================================================================================================================+\r\n| fbb242d98e9d\u2026 | fd59729a977a5326 | llm-proxy   | chat anthropic | 1790.0        | ok     | claude-opus-4-7 \u00b7 1620 tok \u00b7 $0.0213 |\r\n|---------------+------------------+-------------+----------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------|\r\n| fbb242d98e9d\u2026 | d57a02cf8c993896 | api-gateway | POST /v1/chat  | 1850.0        | ok     | -                                    |\r\n+---------------+------------------+-------------+----------------+---------------+--------+--------------------------------------+\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Cross-signal commands cover logs, metrics, SQL, summaries, and correlation.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael query logs --severity error --last 1h --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.7, "o", "No logs found.\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael query metrics --query 'sum by (service) (http_requests)' --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.7, "o", "No series returned.\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael summarize --last 1h --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.0, "o", "Summary \u2014 last 3600s, service: (all)\r\n\r\nTraces\r\n+--------------+-----------+\r\n| Metric       | Value     |\r\n+==========================+\r\n| Spans        | 24        |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Traces       | 15        |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Errors       | 2         |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Error rate   | 8.33%     |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Avg duration | 273.5 ms  |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| p50          | 27.5 ms   |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| p95          | 1644.5 ms |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| p99          | 1836.2 ms |\r\n|--------------+-----------|\r\n| Max          | 1850.0 ms |\r\n+--------------+-----------+\r\n\r\nTop services\r\n+----------------------+-------+------------+----------+\r\n| Service              | Spans | Error Rate | p95 (ms) |\r\n+======================================================+\r\n| api-gateway          | 15    | 6.67%      | 1129.0   |\r\n|----------------------+-------+------------+----------|\r\n| order-service        | 2     | 0.00%      | 747.0    |\r\n|----------------------+-------+------------+----------|\r\n| user-service         | 2     | 0.00%      | 58.3     |\r\n|----------------------+-------+------------+----------|\r\n| notification-service | 1     | 0.00%      | 45.0     |\r\n|----------------------+-------+------------+----------|\r\n| auth-service         | 1     | 0.00%      | 8.0      |\r\n+----------------------+-------+------------+----------+\r\n\r\nTop error operations\r\n+-----------------+---------------------+--------+\r\n| Service         | Operation           | Errors |\r\n+================================================+\r\n| payment-service | payment.charge      | 1      |\r\n|-----------------+---------------------+--------|\r\n| api-gateway     | HTTP POST /checkout | 1      |\r\n+-----------------+---------------------+--------+\r\n\r\nLogs\r\n+----------+-------+\r\n| Severity | Count |\r\n+==================+\r\n| total    | 0     |\r\n|----------+-------|\r\n| error    | 0     |\r\n|----------+-------|\r\n| warn     | 0     |\r\n|----------+-------|\r\n| info     | 0     |\r\n|----------+-------|\r\n| debug    | 0     |\r\n+----------+-------+\r\n\r\nMetrics\r\n+--------------+-------+\r\n| Metric       | Value |\r\n+======================+\r\n| Points       | 0     |\r\n|--------------+-------|\r\n| Unique names | 0     |\r\n+--------------+-------+\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael query sql \"SELECT service, COUNT(*) AS spans, ROUND(AVG(duration_ms),1) AS avg_ms FROM spans GROUP BY service ORDER BY spans DESC LIMIT 5\"\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.9, "o", "+--------+----------------------+-------+\r\n| avg_ms | service              | spans |\r\n+=======================================+\r\n| 227.3  | api-gateway          | 15    |\r\n|--------+----------------------+-------|\r\n| 42.5   | user-service         | 2     |\r\n|--------+----------------------+-------|\r\n| 450.0  | order-service        | 2     |\r\n|--------+----------------------+-------|\r\n| 45.0   | notification-service | 1     |\r\n|--------+----------------------+-------|\r\n| 310.0  | payment-service      | 1     |\r\n+--------+----------------------+-------+\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael correlate --trace 11352dea5f3e... --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.9, "o", "Trace 11352dea5f3ecd0cfd2df94df71fea6f\r\n  spans: 3  errors: 2  duration: 340.0 ms\r\n  services: api-gateway, cart-service, payment-service\r\n  window: 2026-05-29T01:10:23.066412+00:00 \u2192 2026-05-29T01:10:23.406412+00:00\r\n\r\nLogs: (none)\r\n\r\nMetrics: (none in trace window)\r\n"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# The live TUI streams traces as they arrive and lets you drill into waterfalls.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael live --service api-gateway --interval 1\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[1.1, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H\u250c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2510\r\n\u2502 tael live  traces | services | waterfall                                                                             \u2502\r\n\u251c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2524\r\n\u2502 Live Traces                    Service       Operation               Duration   Status                               \u2502\r\n\u2502 -------------------------------------------------------------------------------                                      \u2502\r\n\u2502 | Trace ID      | Span ID          | Service     | Operation               | Duration (ms) | Status |                \u2502\r\n\u2502 | bd126d83ecc7\u2026 | 47725596171304c9 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /ping          | 29.0          | ok     |                \u2502\r\n\u2502 | b31e46c63ce3\u2026 | 7d1b22110ad43eb0 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /config        | 26.0          | ok     |                \u2502\r\n\u2502 | f7f91a1cdf7b\u2026 | 4de0bd8710db79b2 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /users/me      | 23.0          | ok     |                \u2502\r\n\u2502 | a6b7d083745d\u2026 | 03854243a0a801e3 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /api/v1/status | 20.0          | ok     |                \u2502\r\n\u2502 | 46defbae7f50\u2026 | d1ba90386031e207 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /health        | 17.0          | ok     |                \u2502\r\n\u2502 | 4800cbcd97ef\u2026 | 51327bb630e677a2 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /ping          | 14.0          | ok     |                \u2502\r\n\u2502 | cc938f281455\u2026 | b827803a0971900f | api-gateway | HTTP GET /config        | 11.0          | ok     |                \u2502\r\n\u2502 | 9a9e9ae688b2\u2026 | 9b9e9775a9a28342 | api-gateway | HTTP GET /users/me      | 8.0           | ok     |                \u2502\r\n\u2502 Waterfall: HTTP POST /checkout                                                                                       \u2502\r\n\u2502 api-gateway        |\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588| 340ms error                                                  \u2502\r\n\u2502 payment-service    |      \u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588\u2588 | 310ms error                                                  \u2502\r\n\u2502 comments: 2    logs: 1    metrics: 3                                                                                 \u2502\r\n\u2502                                                                                                                      \u2502\r\n\u2502                                                                                                                      \u2502\r\n\u2502                                                                                                                      \u2502\r\n\u2502                                                                                                                      \u2502\r\n\u2502                                                                                                                      \u2502\r\n\u2502                                                                                                                      \u2502\r\n\u2502                                                                                                                      \u2502\r\n\u2502                                                                                                                      \u2502\r\n\u2502                                                                                                                      \u2502\r\n\u251c\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2524\r\n\u2502 j/k move  Enter open trace  f filter  Space pause  q quit                                                            \u2502\r\n\u2514\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2518\r\n"]
[1.2, "o", "q"]
[0.2, "o", "\u001b[2J\u001b[H"]
[0.5, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# Agents can annotate traces, then promote failures into issues and regression cases.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael comment list 11352dea5f3e... --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.8, "o", "[2026-05-29 01:10:28.635275] oncall-bot: Stripe returned 402 - card declined, not a system fault\r\n[2026-05-29 01:10:28.797134] triage-agent (span f40453715c4508d2): Confirmed: customer card expired. Closing.\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael issue create --from-trace 11352dea5f3e... --failure-mode payment_declined --impact medium --summary \"Card decline is a user payment failure, not an outage\"\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.6, "o", "Issue issue_33d1b14e2867488398fe0fbdaba9977a added to trace 11352dea5f3ecd0cfd2df94df71fea6f: Card decline is a user payment failure, not an outage\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael issue list --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.8, "o", "+----------------------------------------+------------------+--------+-----------------+-------------------------------------------------------+----------------------------+\r\n| Issue                                  | Mode             | Impact | Trace           | Summary                                               | Created                    |\r\n+===========================================================================================================================================================================+\r\n| issue_33d1b14e2867488398fe0fbdaba9977a | payment_declined | medium | 11352dea5f3e... | Card decline is a user payment failure, not an outage | 2026-05-29 01:10:31.070138 |\r\n+----------------------------------------+------------------+--------+-----------------+-------------------------------------------------------+----------------------------+\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael eval case add --from-trace 11352dea5f3e... --suite checkout-agent --case-id card-decline-001 --failure-mode payment_declined --source-issue-id <issue-id> --critical-path\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
[0.6, "o", "Eval case checkout-agent/card-decline-001 added from trace 11352dea5f3ecd0cfd2df94df71fea6f\r\n"]
[0.18, "o", "\u001b[1;32m>\u001b[0m tael eval suite inspect checkout-agent --format table\r\n"]
[0.35, "o", ""]
