[0.1, "o", "\r\n"]
[1.8, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36m# -----------------------------------------------------\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[1;37mtael\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n  \u001b[0;90m- Install package: tael-cli, binary: tael\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0;90m- `tael serve` runs the bundled server and storage engine\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0;90m- OTLP traces, logs, metrics, SQL, comments, and correlation\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0;90m- Reliability loop: issues, signals, eval cases, diagnostics\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[0;90m- Trace-native evals with `tael live --eval-run demo-local-wiki-asciinema`\u001b[0m\r\n"]
